<messaging:emailTemplate subject="G&H Request for {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Applicant__r.Name} is pending for your approval (#{!RelatedTo.Name})" recipientType="User" relatedToType="ASI_GnH_Request__c"><messaging:htmlEmailBody ><html>    <body>        <p>Please note the following G&amp;H Request is waiting for your approval/action.<br/>        請注意下列G&amp;H申請文件正待您簽核.</p>        <table>            <tr>                <td>G&amp;H Request No 申請單號</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.Name}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Owner Name 擁有者姓名</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.Owner.Name}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Applicant Name 申請者姓名</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Applicant__r.Name}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Department 部門</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Department__c}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>G&amp;H Type G&amp;H類型</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Type__c}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Recipient Type 受惠對象</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Recipient_Type__c}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Benefit Date 受惠日期</td>                <td>: &nbsp; <apex:outputText value="{0, date, yyyy'-'MMM'-'d}">                                <apex:param value="{!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Benefit_Date__c}" />                            </apex:outputText>                </td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Amount per Recipient 每位參與者費用</td>                <td>: &nbsp; <apex:outputText value="{0, number, ###,###,###,###.##}">                                <apex:param value="{!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Amount_per_Recipient__c}" />                            </apex:outputText>                </td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>PAX 人數</td>                <td>: &nbsp; <apex:outputText value="{0, number, ###,###,###,###}">                                <apex:param value="{!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_PAX__c}" />                            </apex:outputText>                </td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Contract 合約相關</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Contract__c}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Purpose 目的</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Purpose__c}</td>            </tr>        </table>        <p>To approve the G&amp;H Request, click this&nbsp;<apex:outputLink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND('.com/',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!RelatedTo.id}">link</apex:outputLink> or by reply this email with keywords - APPROVE, YES, REJECT, NO<br/>           核准G&amp;H申請單. 回覆此信件請按此&nbsp;<apex:outputLink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND('.com/',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!RelatedTo.id}">連結</apex:outputLink> 或 輸入關鍵字 - 批准,已批准,是,拒絕,已拒絕,否</p>    </body></html></messaging:htmlEmailBody></messaging:emailTemplate>